NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::Sort::Sub - Plugin to use when building
    Sort::Sub::* distribution

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.001 of Dist::Zilla::Plugin::Sort::Sub
    (from Perl distribution Dist-Zilla-Plugin-Sort-Sub), released on
    2019-12-15.

SYNOPSIS
    In dist.ini:

     [Sort::Sub]

DESCRIPTION
    This plugin is to be used when building "Sort::Sub::*" distribution. It
    currently does the following:

    *   Fill-in ABSTRACT from meta's summary

